cranium2003 wrote:
> [...] On my RH9
> i386 arch i got 16kb output from dmesg. how to
> increase it?
man dmesg (parameter -s).
You may also want to increase the kernel buffer size in General Setup -> 
Kernel log buffer size (CONFIG_LOG_BUF_SHIFT).
Michal
